### Health Check - GET detections (basic connectivity test)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/detections
Accept: application/json

###
### Create Detection - POST new drone detection
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/detections
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mac": "60:60:1F:AA:BB:CC",
  "rssi": -50,
  "sensor_location": "Building A - Floor 3",
  "timestamp": "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"
}

